<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>PDAN AI</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#0d1117;
color:white;
}

header{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
padding:20px;
background:#161b22;
}

.logo{
font-size:30px;
font-weight:bold;
color:#00d4ff;
}

button{
padding:10px 20px;
background:#00d4ff;
border:none;
border-radius:8px;
cursor:pointer;
font-weight:bold;
}

.hero{
height:90vh;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:48px;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.hero p{
font-size:20px;
max-width:700px;
margin-bottom:30px;
}

.start{
font-size:18px;
padding:15px 30px;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<header>
<div class="logo">PDAN AI</div>
<button>Login</button>
</header>

<section class="hero">

<h1>The Future of Artificial Intelligence</h1>

<p>
Chat, create images, write documents, solve assignments,
generate code and much more—all in one AI platform.
</p>

<button class="start">
Start Chatting
</button>

</section>

